'''馬來西亞網球公開賽'''曾是一項在[[馬來西亞|馬來西亞]][[吉隆坡|吉隆坡]]舉行的職業[[網球|網球]]巡迴賽<ref name=Profile>{{cite web|work=atpworldtour.com|title=atpworldtour.com tournament profile|url=http://www.atpworldtour.com/Tennis/Tournaments/Kuala-Lumpur.aspx|accessdate=2009-06-26|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090628170238/http://www.atpworldtour.com/Tennis/Tournaments/Kuala-Lumpur.aspx|archivedate=2009-06-28}}</ref>，該賽事创办于2009年，取代了在印度班加罗尔举办的[[翠鸟航空网球公开赛|翠鸟航空网球公开赛]]，<ref>{{cite news|author=atpworldtour.com|title=Kuala Lumpur Confirmed As Newest Stop On ATP World Tour| url = http://www.atpworldtour.com/News/Tennis/2009/06/Kuala-Lumpur-Confirmed-As-Newest-Stop-On-ATP-World-Tour.aspx|date =2009-06-26| access-date =2009-06-26}}</ref>該項賽事的場地為室內硬地，它的等級屬於ATP巡迴賽中的世界巡迴賽250賽。举办地位於[[亚通体育馆|亚通体育馆]]，场地为室内[[硬地球场|硬地球场]]。該項賽事曾經於每年的9月-10月之间举行。這項賽事於2016年被[[成都网球公开赛|成都网球公开赛]]取代。<ref name=Profile/><ref name=Announcement>{{cite web| work =atpworldtour.com| title =Kuala Lumpur Confirmed As Newest Stop On ATP World Tour| url =http://www.atpworldtour.com/News/Tennis/2009/06/Kuala-Lumpur-Confirmed-As-Newest-Stop-On-ATP-World-Tour.aspx| date =2009-06-26| accessdate =2009-06-26| archive-date =2009-06-27| archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20090627231226/http://www.atpworldtour.com/News/Tennis/2009/06/Kuala-Lumpur-Confirmed-As-Newest-Stop-On-ATP-World-Tour.aspx| dead-url =no}}</ref>

